<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />The law of Yahweh is perfect, restoring the soul;</para>

<para style="q1">the testimony of Yahweh is reliable, making the simple wise.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />The instructions of Yahweh are right, making the heart glad;</para>

<para style="q1">the commandment of Yahweh is pure, bringing light to the eyes.</para>
